The '''''Sea Bitch''''' is a longship of the [[Iron Fleet]]. She is assigned to [[Theon Greyjoy]] for raiding along the [[Stony Shore]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[What is Dead May Never Die]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; Its crew of about 20 men are led by Theon in the [[Fall of Winterfell|surprise seizure]] of [[Winterfell]].
